title: Gated Community, Onsite Management, Pet Friendly!
posting_body: ['Designed for modern luxury living, the newly renovated apartment homes at The Meadows offer the lifestyle you desire.', 'Our pet-friendly one and two bedroom apartments in Tacoma, Washington, feature open-concept floor plans with spacious living areas.', 'Sleek stainless-steel appliances, handsome custom cabinetry, and warm wood-style plank flooring are a few of the finishes that add elegance to your space.', 'Each home includes a covered balcony or patio where you can kick back and relax in the fresh air with your pup.', 'Resort-style amenities await at The Meadows.', 'Treat yourself to a refreshing swimming pool, 24-hour fitness center, and a stylish clubhouse with fireplace lounge and complimentary WiFi.', 'Exceptional living begins here.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Close to Restaurants', 'Name Brand Energy-Efficient Appliances', '24-Hour Fitness center', 'Formal Dining Area', 'Pre-Wired for High-Speed Internet Access', 'Online Rental Payments', 'Walk-In Closets', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Close to Schools', 'Individual Hot Water Heaters', 'TV / Theatre Room', 'Stainless-Steel Sink', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
